English.Text: "Your helmsmanship is most impressive!" the Queen calls over to you, as you bring your ship up alongside hers."Meet me at the Cape of Trelawney!"You point your ship towards Trelawney, southernmost point of the Old World, where not fifteen years previous, a great naval victory was won over La Corona by the heroic Admiral Nadasky.The Lap of Victory is there waiting for you, and the Queen receives you warmly aboard. You are finally able to ask why it is she has run away.
